            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Vibgyor Gurugram is truly exceptional in its approach to nurturing children's holistic development. From its outstanding facilities to its dedicated teachers, coaches, and innovative teaching methodologies, every aspect of the school is geared towards creating an enriching environment for students. It's evident that the children genuinely enjoy coming to school, and the positive impact on their development is unmistakable. Vibgyor Gurugram is undoubtedly a remarkable institution dedicated to fostering the growth and success of every child in its care.",
          "publisher": {
