            "name": "Vipul Jain"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-19",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Vibgyor High, Gurgaon provides a wonderful platform of learning and growth for both my kids (currently in grade 8 and 3). We moved from Vibgyor Bangalore in the middle of academic year and with integrated centralised curriculum, it was a smooth transition. The student teacher ratio is 9:1 which makes the learning process very effective and interactive. The school campus is well maintained and highly secured with child friendly infrastructure. The curriculum is very balanced and enhances higher order thinking skills across subjects, in a stress free manner. Loads of activities throughout the year in the form of subject specific activities, competitions and fun fridays. SPA and VIVA competitions give students a wonderful platform to hone their extra curricular skills. Most importantly, the academic team is very experienced, loving and accomodating.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
